288
00:17:18,420 --> 00:17:19,540
They love lively places.

289
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:20,820
So they went there in advance.

290
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:23,940
Your Highness,

291
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:25,380
I'll go and join them.

292
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:27,540
