Yes, Your Highness.

355
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:28,780
Go and find out why.

356
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:29,340
Yes, sir.

357
00:20:32,260 --> 00:20:33,580
The young lady of the Di family
hasn't arrived yet.

