00:29:22,540 --> 00:29:23,740
that you don't like to drink.

484
00:29:30,900 --> 00:29:32,300
You still remember my habits?

485
00:29:36,020 --> 00:29:37,820
Your Highness, I will never forget

486
00:29:39,660 --> 00:29:41,340
