and playing joyful music

671
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:34,780
so that my father can rest in peace
in the underworld.

672
00:39:36,020 --> 00:39:37,060
I hope he knows that the Han family

673
00:39:37,900 --> 00:39:39,020
